header.gameNote: NCAA Women's Championship pres. by Capital One - Hemisfair Region - Semifinal

videos.headline: Owusu, Collins run give-and-go for Maryland bucket
videos.description: Ashley Owusu inbounds the ball to Mimi Collins, who sends it back to Owusu for a layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Owusu, Collins run give-and-go for Maryland bucket) 2021/03/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Maryland answers Texas' bucket with an and-1 lay-in
videos.description: Audrey Warren scores for Texas, but Ashley Owusu tosses a long pass to Diamond Miller for an and-1 layup for Maryland.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Maryland answers Texas' bucket with an and-1 lay-in) 2021/03/28

videos.headline: Miller gets crafty with a spinning layup
videos.description: Diamond Miller gets inside and somehow gets the tough lay-in to go for Maryland.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Miller gets crafty with a spinning layup) 2021/03/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas forces late turnover, scores transition layup for lead
videos.description: Lauren Ebo forces a turnover, which leads to Kyra Lambert scoring the go-ahead bucket in Texas' upset of Maryland.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Texas forces late turnover, scores transition layup for lead) 2021/03/28 ESHEET
